HEADWORD: Tegular
<hw>Teg"u*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>tegularis</ets>, from L. <ets>tegula</ets> a tile. See
<er>Tile</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to a tile; resembling a
tile, or arranged like tiles; consisting of tiles; <as>as, a
<ex>tegular</ex> pavement</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Teg"u*lar*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

